  "keyFeatures": [
    "Gesture-driven edge swipe with axis locking — works alongside ScrollView, List, and Form",
    "Left and right direction support via SlideMenuDirection",
    "Configurable edge detection zone width to avoid conflicts with interactive content",
    "Tap-to-dismiss overlay with customizable color and opacity",
    "Matches device display corner radius for a native feel",
    "Full customization through SwiftUI environment modifiers — no bindings needed",
    "SlideMenuButton reads toggle action from environment automatically",
    "Zero external dependencies, Swift Package Manager distribution"
  ],
